Package com.ibm.team.repository.client

Provides the main client-side-only APIs for the Repository component.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICertificateHandler
    Handler for validating the certificate presented by a server when establishing an SSL connection.
    IContentManager
    Methods for storing and retrieving contents from the repository.
    IContentManagerInputStreamProvider
    An interface for a class that can continue opening an InputStream on the same resource for the benefit of the content manager.
    IContentManagerSession
    Encapsulates a file transfer session for the IContentManager.
    IContributorManager
    A contributor manager for a particular team repository.
    IDeferredSecuredLoginInfo  
    IDeferredSecuredLoginInfo.ISecuredLoginPropertiesCallback
    Defers the fetching of the secured login properties when ready.
    IDownloadHandler
    Accepts events regarding a download being managed by a IContentManagerSession.
    IExternalUserRegistryManager  
    IItemManager
    An item manager for a particular team repository.
    ILicenseClient  
    ILoginHandler2
    Handler for acquiring user id and password when a repository is about to be logged in to with #login(), or whenever the repository decides to challenge an already logged-in client (as determined by that repository's security policies).
    ILoginInfo2
    ILoginInfo2 provides the functionality of encapsulating credentials that are custom to the method that is being used and also provides a way to use those credentials by passing those off to ITeamServer.
    IOAuthClientLibrary
    A library that helps ease the use of OAuth connections between two team repositories.
    IRetryPolicy
    A policy describing what failed requests can be retried and any limitations on the retry (example how many times they can be retried and if the client should back off to give the server a chance to recover before retrying).
    ISharedItemChangeEvent
    Represents an event describing a change to a shared item.
    ISharedItemChangeListener
    Listener for changes to shared items.
    IStatistics
    Statistics data for a particular team repository.
    ITeamRepository
    Represents a team repository.
    ITeamRepository.ILoginHandler
    Handler for acquiring user id and password when a repository is about to be logged in to with #login(), or whenever the repository decides to challenge an already logged-in client (as determined by that repository's security policies).
    ITeamRepository.ILoginHandler.ILoginInfo
    Simple data structure encapsulating both a user id and a password.
    ITeamRepository.ILoginParticipant
    Login participant interface to be implemented by clients that are interested in contributing to the login/logout function.
    ITeamRepositoryService
    Service for establishing contact with team repositories.
    ITeamRepositoryService.IRepositoryServiceListener
    Listener interface used to listen to repository additions and removals from the team repository service.
    IUploadHandler
    Accepts events regarding a upload being managed by a IContentManagerSession and provides data needed to upload content.

Package com.ibm.team.repository.client Description

Provides the main client-side-only APIs for the Repository component.

Package Specification

The API is used by a client to communicate with a team server/repository.

Main entry class is TeamPlatform.
